Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.13,0:01:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.53,0:02:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.14,0:02:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三十一话\N传达不到的相思\N剑心的出发旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.95,0:02:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.28,0:02:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天太晚睡了 再让我睡一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.12,0:02:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起床了懒鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还有心情睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.92,0:02:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道今天是什么日子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.86,0:02:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是五月十四日\N是大久保大人要来的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.70,0:02:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是大久保这个混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.27,0:02:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.60,0:02:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 我们去找剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 就是今天吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论大久保大人 如何给他压力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.36,0:03:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都会支持他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.79,0:03:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心的意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他什么也没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.30,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.21,0:03:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚这里有萤火虫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一闪一闪好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初夏的萤火虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.62,0:03:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年会是温暖的一年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了这个季节 萤火虫就会出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心没看过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.89,0:03:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 剑心来这里还不到一年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.30,0:03:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但好像已住了好久似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.60,0:03:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不让剑心离开\N我要他一直住在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次带剑心看萤火虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.88,0:03:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.61,0:03:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今晚去抓萤火虫 好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定哦剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.08,0:03:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我.. 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.76,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还有心情在这里散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.10,0:04:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可不可正经点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心这个人就是心肠太软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.74,0:04:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝不会让你受人摆布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.21,0:04:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别被大久保那混蛋\N美丽的谎言给骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 你好像很讨厌政府官员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.79,0:04:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果大久保 是自私自利的政客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.39,0:04:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤就不会甘心帮他做事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个坏蛋警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.73,0:04:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们联手 才有真正的正义存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.41,0:04:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤是个 充满正义感的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使到了明治时代 他仍然没有改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.15,0:05:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立誓要消灭黑暗中的邪恶力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实他是个值得交的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.65,0:05:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.39,0:05:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.06,0:05:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们讨厌他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.36,0:05:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 藤田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.90,0:05:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么新撰组的成员\N总是做出令人讨厌的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.68,0:05:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道绯村决定了没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.29,0:05:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定去找大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.43,0:05:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 他不是要来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.23,0:05:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保大人是个忙碌的人\N还是我去比较快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.41,0:06:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.78,0:06:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你一定要去的话\N我就给你喝下这个迷药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.32,0:06:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你全身动不了 你就哪也去不成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小惠你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.93,0:06:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 你什么时候学会这个玩意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.17,0:06:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的独家秘方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.94,0:06:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是决定去一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.94,0:06:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道大久保住哪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已去向地方官打听过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.88,0:06:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了纪尾井山边就可以找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.82,0:06:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 你会愈帮愈忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.50,0:07:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.51,0:07:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心已在神谷道场住习惯了\N不会随便离开我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.04,0:07:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他该不会答应大久保吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.18,0:07:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会让他去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.52,0:07:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心去哪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他什么时候回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.06,0:07:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.27,0:07:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的就能带给国家和平 人民幸福吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.80,0:07:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的会议真冗长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.57,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是被内务省杂事给担搁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.04,0:08:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到了绯村的住处 都已天黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道绯村决定如何了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 一定要说服他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果绯村不愿意来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家就要灭亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心别人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,担心你自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的命快不保了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.43,0:08:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄叫我告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.04,0:08:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别大费周章想叫绯村剑心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.01,0:08:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本 以后交给他接管就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是石川县士族 岛田一良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是长连豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奸贼大久保快出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车夫解决了大家快上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保快出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经被杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.97,0:09:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被人捷足先登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.38,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经向报社发布暗杀令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就当做是我们杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岛田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.49,0:09:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正也没人看见 就说大久保是我们杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.80,0:09:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保卿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.77,0:09:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.15,0:10:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想有此下场 你就少管闲事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,号外号外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.82,0:10:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保内务大人被暗杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.72,0:10:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.16,0:10:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在纪尾井山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.70,0:10:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的精神领袖被刺杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.30,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是对政府不满的石川县士族干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.05,0:11:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是志志雄的阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.72,0:11:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他早就得知有人要刺杀大人\N他利用他们杀掉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.36,0:11:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己却不用出面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.93,0:11:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后藉此分化人心\N再慢慢瓦解政府力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.75,0:11:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是福岛县的山吉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是最后见到\N大久保大人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.95,0:11:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于要赶回东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.32,0:11:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天清晨特别提早\N到官邸去面见大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.49,0:11:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到却发生这样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.83,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明治维新虽然已过了十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.26,0:12:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但推动的情形\N却不如预想中的顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.84,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稳固国家基础\N最少需要三十年的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.08,0:12:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一个十年是创业期\N第二个十年是发展期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.92,0:12:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是安定国家最重要的时期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.15,0:12:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此才能完完全全\N成为一个理想的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.43,0:12:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何谓理想的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.37,0:12:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是民主国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民主国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.53,0:12:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是由人民统治的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.37,0:12:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是从古至今\N日本一直在努力完成的大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.91,0:12:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为民主国家之时\N也就是维新成功之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.05,0:12:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个理想也太大了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.66,0:13:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要大久保健在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人不解的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.20,0:13:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常沉默的大人\N今早却异常热情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.88,0:13:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与我大谈他的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已预料到\N自己将遭预不测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.35,0:13:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许他想为国家\N尽自己最后的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.86,0:13:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川路好像十分悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.73,0:13:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他对大久保大人非常忠贞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过不只川路该伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.54,0:13:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去了大久保大人\N也是国家的损失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.18,0:13:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久后 政局一定会开始大乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.52,0:14:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄也一定会趁机搅乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.56,0:14:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤 你打算怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.70,0:14:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一条路 回到京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解决志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.81,0:14:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,号外大久保大人被暗杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有大事发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会不会又发生战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府说不定会完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维新就此结束了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政局又要开始混乱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.00,0:14:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想再回到那个时代了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.40,0:14:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世间再也没有正义可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.44,0:14:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成民主国家就是维新成功之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.51,0:15:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要大久保健在 理想一定会成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.78,0:15:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久后 政局一定会开始大乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.45,0:15:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄也一定会趁机搅乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无能的政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.12,0:15:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我宁可被处死 也不要剑心去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.16,0:15:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心去杀志志雄会有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.37,0:15:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心已不再杀人了\N我们绝不让他去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.94,0:15:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江山易改本性难移 武士就是武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.75,0:15:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到死都不会变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.19,0:15:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你一生 都无法改变的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.27,0:15:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沾了血的双手 岂能轻易放下屠刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.81,0:16:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武士到死都是武士 拔刀斋才是真正的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在决斗中求生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.21,0:16:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.65,0:16:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时代已开始变动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.66,0:16:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再躲起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.68,0:16:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚还有人要看病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.82,0:16:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷快回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.12,0:16:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会赶回来见剑心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.99,0:16:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送你到停车场吧\N这么晚了一个女孩子不安全的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.64,0:17:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心回来我会通知你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道剑心在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.28,0:17:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.72,0:17:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心就不必去京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.03,0:17:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找他看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.56,0:17:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的萤火虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.91,0:18:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.62,0:18:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.42,0:18:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保今早被暗杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.76,0:18:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是志志雄派人干的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.86,0:18:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再任他为非做歹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定要去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.11,0:18:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又要回去做武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.58,0:18:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.82,0:19:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这十年来 我一直要让自己 忘记是个武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.76,0:19:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道我的身体里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.83,0:19:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是流着武士的血液
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.64,0:19:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你曾告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.37,0:19:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何你都不会再杀人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.01,0:19:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是剑心 不是武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.08,0:19:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也曾说过 只要大家有危难时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.25,0:19:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是会再拿起武士刀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.27,0:19:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次遇见你时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.07,0:19:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉我 不在乎我的过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.57,0:19:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日子久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.92,0:20:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至忘记 自己曾是剑客的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.97,0:20:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.70,0:20:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是流浪人 我会再回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.79,0:21:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明治十一年五月十四日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.29,0:21:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村剑心决心重回江湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.50,0:21:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失于漆黑的夜色中
